.4216, 144.4954, 146.8481, 146.5087, 146.942, 147.7784, 146.5628, 147.5458, 148.3097, 148.89, 148.5087, 148.7991, 148.877, 149.8138, 150.3429, 151.7585, 147.4527, 146.19, 147.4287, 147.6742, 147.0008, 147.8551, 147.439, 146.6414, 147.5372, 147.1984, 148.0263, 147.5526, 148.3003, 148.0892, 148.7162, 147.9679, 144.9166, 145.5976, 143.9459, 138.3754, 138.257, 141.4203, 136.3711, 136.3016, 136.2022, 137.3138, 136.9823, 135.4582, 134.3188, 134.1552, 132.4173, 130.8953, 133.5221, 132.6426, 132.3812, 136.1578, 137.614, 138.7309, 135.6828, 135.0728, 134.8853, 137.754, 135.595, 137.398, 137.3335, 138.3056, 137.7852, 137.8773, 138.9116, 138.1433, 137.8068, 136.6669, 135.2937, 135.0852, 134.6112, 132.7962, 133.1297, 133.6737, 132.9028, 134.7055, 136.0667, 136.0271, 136.0896, 135.4445, 137.4394, 135.1619, 134.8044, 136.3988], "summary_html": "<h1>负债市值比 (Debt/Market Cap) — 商品期货代理实现</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>Bhandari (1988) 在 JF 上证明：A 股层面 TL/MV（负债/市值）是一个稳定的截面定价因子，高负债率公司因 financial leverage risk premium 享受更高的 expected return。原研报针对股票，商品期货没有直接的\"债务\"和\"股本\"概念。</p>\n<p>本复现按 \"融资负担 / 市值\" 的思路构建三通道商品 proxy：</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>通道</th><th>TL proxy</th><th>MV proxy</th><th>含义</th></tr><tr><td>lev_receipt</td><td>receipt（仓单数量）</td><td>opi * close</td><td>仓单 = 债务融资型仓储库存</td></tr><tr><td>lev_inv</td><td>inventory_lp + inventory_sp</td><td>opi * close</td><td>库存占用现金 = 供给端杠杆</td></tr><tr><td>lev_member</td><td>abs(memberdiff20)</td><td>opi</td><td>大单席位净持仓错配 = 机构杠杆</td></tr></table></div>\n<p>按 Bhandari 风险溢价：高 leverage proxy → 做多。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.78</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>2.9%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>3.7%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-6.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.01</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3420</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.99</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.75</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.8 / 1.16</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.62</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.45</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.19</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.3</span></td><td>1.46</td><td>0.03</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.57</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.39</span></td><td>1.2</td><td>1.3</td><td>1.44</td><td>0.36</td><td>0.82</td><td>1.92</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.97</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>opi</code></td><td>持仓量</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 5 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 5 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3422</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>99.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>41.3</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\mathrm{MV}_{i,t} = \\mathrm{opi}_{i,t} \\cdot \\mathrm{close}_{i,t}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\mathrm{lev}^{(k)}_{i,t} = \\mathrm{TL}^{(k)}_{i,t} / \\mathrm{MV}_{i,t}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\overline{\\mathrm{lev}}^{(k)}_{i,t} = \\mathrm{MA}_{w}(\\mathrm{lev}^{(k)}_{i,t})</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">r^{(k,w)}_{i,t} = \\mathrm{CSPctRank}_t(\\overline{\\mathrm{lev}}^{(k)}_{\\cdot,t}) \\in [0,1]</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\mathrm{pos}^{(k,w,h)}_{i,t} = 2 (r^{(k,w)}_{i,t} - 0.5) \\in [-1, +1], \\quad \\text{rebalance every } h \\text{ days}</div>\n<p>其中 k ∈ {receipt, inv, member}，w ∈ {10, 20, 60}，h ∈ {5, 10, 20}。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<ul><li>R1：旧 spec 用 basis + inventory_lp 拼凑成 leverage，逻辑与 Bhandari 无关，靠 inv_lp 单通道侥幸得 Sharpe 0.99；spec_complete gate 失败（signal/position/execution/risk/contract 全空）。</li>\n<li>R2：spec 内容未补齐，仍卡在 spec_complete。</li>\n<li>R3 (本轮)：重写 spec → (a) 补齐五大文本字段 + contract_layer (roll_rule / adjustment)；(b) 重新设计 TL proxy / MV proxy 三通道 (receipt / inventory / member) + 多窗口 ts_mean + 截面 rank + rebalance_hold；(c) 共 32 个原始变体，扩展归一化后 96 个变体。5 个 gate 全通过，best Sharpe 0.969 (lev_inv20_h5_raw)。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li>数据频率：日频</li>\n<li>品种范围：59 个商品（含 inventory_lp / receipt / memberdiff20 字段的品种）</li>\n<li>持仓周期：5 个交易日 rebalance</li>\n<li>数据要求：receipt 非空率 86%，inventory_lp/sp 80%，memberdiff20 62%；2016 年之前持仓字段稀缺，因此 2012-2015 表现较弱（全期 Sharpe 0.78 &lt; 样本内 0.99）。</li>\n<li>已知局限：原文针对股票，商品代理是结构性近似；inventory 占主导通道意味着本质上更接近一个供给端因子，而不是严格的财务杠杆因子。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9994</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.81s</li>\n</ul>"}